      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "Anyone here have full SOC designs and having issues with very long synthesis times? Our same design for fpga on vivado takes 15-30 minutes to synth, but on yosys we’re seeing 12+ hours despite enabling multi threading and other usual suspects. Is this a known issue?\n\nI opened a PR with yosys to merge some optimizations and it was rejected because it was “AI assisted” and I must admit the attitude was very disappointing despite providing follow ups, asking questions, etc.",
      "author": {
        "id": "591049455499739147",
        "name": "crockpotveggies",
        "discriminator": "0000",
        "nickname": "J-Lo",
        "color": null,
        "isBot": false,
        "roles": [],
